# Investment Timeline and Funding Options

**Flexible financing approaches for transformation investment**

| Funding Option | Amount | Terms | Advantages | Considerations |
|----------------|--------|-------|------------|----------------|
| **Internal Cash Flow** | $2.0M | Pay-as-you-go | No external obligations | Slower implementation |
| **Credit Line** | $1.2M | 3-year term | Flexible drawdown | Interest costs |
